title: 212: Scout's Notebook, Christian Kirk Interview
itunes:title: 212: Scout's Notebook, Christian Kirk Interview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks dive into Bucky's latest Scout's Notebook to analyze Washington's defense and Tyreek Hill (4:00). The guys also ask which franchise will bounce back from a rough Week 3 (12:00). DJ and Bucky then interview A&M's electric wide receiver Christian Kirk (18:20) before they make this week's college football picks (29:00).
